High-level architecture:
Enterprise Network
│
├── Telemetry Agent (Linux)
│ └── Collects network metrics
│
├── API Gateway (FastAPI)
│ ├── Auth & RBAC
│ ├── Telemetry ingestion
│ └── Enterprise APIs
│
├── Telemetry Processor
│ └── Aggregation & SLA metrics
│
└── Customer / Partner Consumers
├── Dashboards
├── NOCs
└── Automation Systems
